{"tid":626841,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【四月岡媽x BONES原創新番】Hisone與Masotan","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T02:01:10.000Z","uid":45373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e0083c35a4df0a105914a2289edc7357d310f7b7","tid":626841,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.nautiljon.com/images/anime/00/66/hisone_to_masotan_7466.jpg?1523487455\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nautiljon.com%2Fimages%2Fanime%2F00%2F66%2Fhisone_to_masotan_7466.jpg%3F1523487455&h=a44071fc&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>STORY</em><br />\n「我與你一同飛向天空。」<br />\n甘粕ひそね是最近開始在航空自衛隊岐阜基地任職的新人，過於率直而總是無意識地傷害他人，對此感到疲憊不堪的她，選擇成為任期限定的自衛官，但命運的邂逅徹底改變了她的人生。被秘藏在基地中、偽裝成戰鬥機的龍選中了ひそね，並和她一起飛向天空。<br />\n就這樣，搭乘「OTF（變態飛翔生命體）」的飛行要員，成為了ひそね的工作。甚至能左右國家命運的龍，究竟隱藏著怎樣的秘密&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n<em>STAFF</em><br />\n原　作：BONES、樋口真嗣、岡田麿里<br />\n總監督：樋口真嗣<br />\n監　督：小林　寬<br />\n系列構成：岡田麿里<br />\n角色原案：青木俊直<br />\n角色設計：伊藤嘉之<br />\n主要機械設計：河森正治<br />\n怪物概念設計：小山重人<br />\n軍事考證：小柳啓伍<br />\n美術設計：平澤晃弘<br />\n美術監督：金子雄司<br />\n色彩設計：小針裕子<br />\n攝影監督：佐佐木康太<br />\n3DCG監督：安東容太<br />\n編集：奧田浩史<br />\n音樂：岩崎太整<br />\n音響監督：山田陽<br />\n音響效果：野口透<br />\n動畫製作：BONES<br />\n<br />\n<em>CAST</em><br />\n甘粕ひそね：久野美咲<br />\n貝崎名緒：黑澤朋世<br />\n星野絵瑠：河瀨茉希<br />\n絹番莉莉子：新井里美<br />\n日登美真弓：名塚佳織<br />\n樋本貞：朴璐美<br />\n小此木榛人：梶裕貴<br />\n財投豊：徳本恭敏<br />\n柿保令美：釘宮理惠<br />\n幾嶋博己：諏訪部順一<br />\n曾曾田弘：中田讓治</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/eHdeaxvdrFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeHdeaxvdrFc&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=eab2b021\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eHdeaxvdrFc</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://hisomaso.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhisomaso.com%2F&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=cb8e4c34\" target=\"_blank\">http://hisomaso.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hisomaso_anime?lang=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhisomaso_anime%3Flang%3Dzh-tw&d=%2BI%2BMj8jsIKeOGRJVcOuxUv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bce8e69a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hisomaso_anime?lang=zh-tw</a></div><br />\n<br />\n變態飛翔生命體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7524d38fbc0c538c8d617ac08b05fbfd7c5c189","tid":626841,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"d女咁既樣"},{"pid":"42094f0d132d9b0235dfedf5ca2e2802a945f478","tid":626841,"uid":46155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/12/205419_ec2b47c2a16d53a2bd7699d2e8d66868.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F12%2F205419_ec2b47c2a16d53a2bd7699d2e8d66868.gif&h=b6b0035e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e345b489c725f8109f56cc3f85f1290a31056","tid":626841,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"岡媽睇定啲先"},{"pid":"03e267c2ebe3a0db526778b92e495a5f9833d3df","tid":626841,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7524d38fbc0c538c8d617ac08b05fbfd7c5c189","tid":626841,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"d女咁既樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"sorry 禾是因為睇到個人設 先有留意套野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1ff490723f3eabb6e308383d980ed97dbb09d5","tid":626841,"uid":46551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"岡媽+河森<img src=\"/assets/faces/l